            <![CDATA[
                <h3>New Features</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>GlowBar:</strong> A brand new addition to your menu bar experience.</li>
                    <li><strong>Item Count Badges:</strong> Keep track of your items with customizable badges right in the menu bar.</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Drag & Drop Enhancements</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Precision Control:</strong> Refactored drag path calculations for pinpoint accuracy during item organization.</li>
                    <li><strong>Improved Stability:</strong> Adjusted sensitivity with a 50% overlap threshold to prevent accidental moves.</li>
                    <li><strong>Visual Feedback:</strong> Added clear visual cues during drag operations to improve usability.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]>
